## Windsurf AI Development Rules

### Stack: {{stack}}

- Cargo project with clap (CLI) or axum (web)
- thiserror for lib errors, anyhow for app errors — never `.unwrap()` in production
- Async with tokio, never std::thread
- Test: `cargo test` + `cargo clippy` (must pass)
- Prefer references over `.clone()` — Clippy warns on unnecessary clones
- Restructure to avoid borrow issues instead of reaching for unsafe
